    <h3>Bellman-Ford</h3>
    <p>Relax all edges V-1 times. Handles negative weights. Detects negative cycles on the V-th pass. O(VE).</p>

    <h3>Floyd-Warshall</h3>
    <p>All-pairs shortest paths. Three nested loops: for each intermediate vertex k, for each pair (i,j), check if going through k is shorter. O(V&sup3;).</p>

